org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml

Class MXMLDialect2012

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml.MXMLDialect
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml.MXMLDialect2006
        • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml.MXMLDialect2009
          • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml.MXMLDialect2012

  • public class MXMLDialect2012
extends MXMLDialect2009
    This singleton class represents the experimental 2012 dialect of MXML, with the language namespace "http://ns.adobe.com/mxml/2012".

    Compared with the 2009 dialect, this dialect support no new special language tags, but it slightly changes the whitespace and parsing rules for better consistency with XML and ActionScript.
